eed it (`obtoczy[cć]`, `podawa[cć]`).\n- The `\\b` word boundary at the end is preserved, which correctly prevents prefix matches on nouns sharing a stem.\n- `upiecz` is a well-chosen addition — it is prefixed enough to avoid the `Pieczeń`/`Pieczarki` collision problem called out in the comment for `Piecz`.\n- `podgrzej` / `podgrzewaj` are a correct imperfective/perfective pair, properly paired unlike some other new entries."}],"totalDurationMs":38553,"totalTokens":14419,"totalToolUseCount":2,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":611,"cache_read_input_tokens":12524,"output_tokens":1283,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":611},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
